# React Doctor Health Check (React-only)

When asked to run React Doctor, health check, or dead code analysis, follow the instructions in:
`.claude/skills/react-doctor/SKILL.md`

## Quick Reference

**Usage:** Run on any React project to get a 0-100 health score.
- `full` — full scan (default)
- `diff [base]` — diff-only scan against base branch
- `fix` — auto-fix safe issues

**React-only:** Automatically skips Vue projects.

**BANNED:**
- Running on Vue-only projects
- Fabricating diagnostics

For full protocol: read `.claude/skills/react-doctor/SKILL.md`
